data.text: Khoy (Persian: خوی‎; also Romanized as Khoi, Khvoy, Khowy, Khuy, and Xoy), (Azerbaijani: Xoy); (Armenian: Խոյ) is a city in and the capital of Khoy County, West Azerbaijan Province, Iran.
